 Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mrz 2022) 4aPoetik. 4aRomania. 4aRuine. 4aÄsthetik. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / European / General.2bisacsh  aRomance-speaking world.  aRuins.  aaesthetics.  apoetics.1 aBaum, Constanze, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBéreiziat-Lang, Stephanie, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDadaş, Şirin, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHiergeist, Teresa, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aIzzo, Sara, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLombardi, Giulia, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLombardi, Giulia, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aLoy, Benjamin, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aOberto, Simona, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aOberto, Simona, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aOster, Angela, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRieger, Angelica, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSchneider, Lars, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSteurer, Hannah, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aStrohmaier, Paul, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aStrohmaier, Paul, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt0 cEPUBz97831107578660 cprintz978311075771240uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311075781140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110757811423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110757811/original  aEBA_CL_AD  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  